Nehemiah prays and continues the work; [Neh
4:7](../../../bib/kjv/neh004.htm#007.md), Understanding the wrath and
secrets of the enemy, he sets a watch; [Neh
4:13](../../../bib/kjv/neh004.htm#013.md), He arms the labourers; [Neh
4:19](../../../bib/kjv/neh004.htm#019.md), and gives military precepts.

